frames.caption: A solitary tree stands majestically on a small grassy hill, illuminated by a soft, ethereal light against a deep blue sky. Its vibrant green leaves create a striking contrast with the dark surroundings, reflecting beautifully on the calm water below. The scene is framed by additional trees, adding depth and a sense of tranquility.
frames.description: The scene depicts a serene, natural setting at night, with a focus on a single illuminated tree on a hill by a body of water. The atmosphere is peaceful and almost magical, enhanced by the reflection of the tree in the water and the surrounding darkness.

frames.caption: A luminous tree stands majestically on a small grassy hill, its vibrant green leaves glowing against a deep blue night sky. The tree's reflection shimmers on the calm water below, creating a serene and magical atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a tranquil night setting with a single, radiant tree at the center of a small island surrounded by water. The glowing leaves and their reflection create a mystical ambiance.
